- Sure.

67
00:06:02,021 --> 00:06:04,398
How well do you know my daughter?

68
00:06:04,481 --> 00:06:07,026
We've been dating for two years.

69
00:06:07,109 --> 00:06:11,822
If you need to ask me about this, I
have a sense you don't know Sydney.

70
00:06:12,156 --> 00:06:16,076
I love your daughter, I want
to marry her. That's why I'm calling.

71
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:20,080
First of all, the truth is,
this is just a courtesy call.

72
00:06:20,164 --> 00:06:25,127
Like saying to a neighbour, "We're
having a party, if that's all right."

73
00:06:25,211 --> 00:06:28,839
