497
01:00:20,070 --> 01:00:22,990
There's some more coffee
and something to eat.

498
01:00:28,495 --> 01:00:31,832
Just let Mr Weiss know
if you need anything else.

499
01:00:31,916 --> 01:00:34,501
A new pen. This one's dying.

500
01:00:36,545 --> 01:00:38,839
Thanks.

501
01:01:11,288 --> 01:01:14,208
- This could be interesting.
- So am I in?

502
01:01:15,000 --> 01:01:17,628
Not yet.
They're reviewing your statement.

503
01:01:17,711 --> 01:01:20,339
- It's... You wrote a lot.
- I know.

504
01:01:20,422 --> 01:01:22,842
I mean, it's like Tolstoy-long.

505
01:01:23,551 --> 01:01:26,387
Devlin says
it could take weeks to verify.

506
01:01:26,470 --> 01:01:29,932
But I know we could use
another double agent in SD-6.

507
01:01:30,558 --> 01:01:34,019
We'll be in touch. I'll get you
out of here, keep you concealed.

508
01:01:34,103 --> 01:01:36,689
- Why shake your head?
- You said "another".

509
01:01:36,772 --> 01:01:39,108
So?

510
01:01:39,191 --> 01:01:43,404
So if you had one, you wouldn't
tell me until I was authenticated.

511
01:01:43,487 --> 01:01:47,825
- Unless I had an instinct about you.
- You don't have another double.

512
01:01:47,908 --> 01:01:51,287
- We might.
- But you want me to believe you do.

513
01:01:51,370 --> 01:01:55,708
So if I aim to be a triple agent,
I'll report an existing mole,

514
01:01:55,791 --> 01:01:57,918
to upset the balance of my agency.

515
01:01:59,128 --> 01:02:01,839
- I'm not trying to play you.
- We'll see.

516
01:02:03,173 --> 01:02:05,176
I have an instinct.

517
01:02:13,392 --> 01:02:16,645
You need a dentist. Do you have one?
I can get you a name.

518
01:02:16,729 --> 01:02:18,939
I'm all right.

519
01:02:21,233 --> 01:02:22,693
I'll be right back.

520
01:03:15,412 --> 01:03:19,667
- I wanted to say I was sorry.
- You don't have to.

521
01:03:21,710 --> 01:03:24,421
I'm back at work.
I guess you know that.

522
01:03:24,922 --> 01:03:27,091
I meant sorry about Danny.

523
01:03:28,175 --> 01:03:30,469
There was nothing I could do.

524
01:03:30,553 --> 01:03:33,514
I'd like to be alone,
if you don't mind.

525
01:03:36,934 --> 01:03:39,144
I know what it's like
to lose someone.

526
01:03:39,228 --> 01:03:43,524
I don't know what you expect.
Just because we're on the same side,

527
01:03:43,607 --> 01:03:49,238
just because I know the truth now,
it doesn't change a thing between us.

528
01:03:51,323 --> 01:03:54,243
I accept what I'm doing now
because I have to.

529
01:03:56,745 --> 01:03:59,498
That doesn't mean
I have to accept you.

530
01:04:05,713 --> 01:04:09,049
I asked Devlin
if I could come tell you myself.

531
01:04:11,552 --> 01:04:14,471
They verified your statement.
You're in.

532
01:04:17,183 --> 01:04:18,767
I read what you wrote.

533
01:04:20,102 --> 01:04:24,273
I appreciate your not naming me.
That was... kind.

534
01:04:30,112 --> 01:04:31,822
You're CIA.

535
01:04:32,615 --> 01:04:35,743
You don't know
how dangerous this is, Sydney,

536
01:04:35,826 --> 01:04:38,037
doing what I do.

537
01:04:39,079 --> 01:04:41,498
I wish you'd taken me up
on Switzerland.

538
01:04:42,833 --> 01:04:46,462
How do I know
what you're telling me is the truth?

539
01:04:50,341 --> 01:04:53,636
I guess we'll just have to learn
to trust each other.

540
01:05:32,049 --> 01:05:33,717
Hello?



